Privacy Policy — Unchained Money
                                                                                                                                                                                                           
                                                                                                                        
  Data Collection                                                                                                       
  Unchained Money does not collect, store, or transmit any personal data to external servers. All financial information you
   enter — including income, expenses, loans, and assets — is stored exclusively on your device.                        
                                                                                                                        
  No Data Sharing                                                                                                       
  We do not share, sell, or transfer your data to any third parties. There are no analytics SDKs, advertising           
  frameworks, or tracking tools embedded in this app.                                                                   
                                                                                                                        
  Local Storage                                                                                                         
  Your data is saved locally on your device in the app's private storage. This data persists until you either clear it  
  within the app (Profile → Clear All Data) or uninstall the app. No cloud backup or sync is performed.                 
                                                                                                                        
  No Account Required                                                                                                   
  Unchained Money does not require you to create an account, sign in, or provide any identifying information such as your
  name, email, or phone number.                                                                                         
                                                                                                                      
  Third-Party Services                                                                                                  
  This app does not integrate with any banks, payment processors, or financial institutions. It does not access your  
  bank accounts, credit cards, or any external financial data.                                                          
   
  Children's Privacy                                                                                                    
  This app does not knowingly collect any data from children under 13. Since no data leaves the device, there is no risk
   of personal information being collected from minors.                                                                 
  
  Changes to This Policy                                                                                                
  We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page with an updated     
  revision date.                                                                                                        
  
